// How do you send a plain text email using configuration defaults for SMTP server, with a subject of 'Hello' and body of 'This is a test email', and sending it to John Doe / john@doe.com?
mail.smtp.send
   message
      to
         .
            email:john@doe.com
            name:John Doe
      subject:Hello
      entity:text/plain
         content:This is a test email
